, Tokushima Prefecture. * {{ill|Tenjinja (Tokushima)|en|12=draft|12=draft}}
- Located in Kitamiya, Tokushima. * {{ill|Tenjinja (Tokushima-Iritacho)|en}}
- Located in Irita, Tokushima.
== Kyushu Region == * - Located in Kamiaru, {{ill|Itoshima, Fukuoka|en|12=draft|12=draft}}
, Fukuoka Prefecture.
